From: Yuval Mintz <yuvalmin@broadcom.com>
Date: Sun, 13 Jan 2013 18:14:56 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 07/27] bnx2x: Added nvram personalities support
git-commit: 4ba7699be9e038b3f4d4857ef5d2150ebd9a7b60
References: FATE#313915 bnc#790597
Patch-mainline: v3.9-rc1

When a device is configured to act as either iscsi or fcoe
device in its nvram, prevent the other from being misused by
preventing its activation in the driver.

